<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5363216>
    dc:description "Fig. 41. Microporodes S. Endrödy-Younga, 1978 and Palmopria S. Endrödy-Younga, 1978: a – P. elaeidis S. Endrödy-Younga, 1978; b–e – M. dispar (Murray, 1864). a, b – male habitus (a – length 2.5 mm; b – length 2.6 mm); c – ovipositor; d–e – male genitalia. Drawing a modified from ENDRÖDY-YOUNGA (1978); drawings c–e modified from COOPER (1974). Drawings c–e: refer to COOPER (1974) for scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5363216/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

